title: PABEKH EATING PLACE
review: Pabekh is also a refreshment providing place.  Good quality of food is provided here.  This is situated in Deviketh near Rishikesh offering quality food.

title: Actually a restaurant
review: Pabekh is a nice restaurant in the holy city of Rishikesh and has a wide variety of eating options for veg lovers.

title: small nice restaurant
review: a small nice local restaurant serving good vegetarian dishes in rishikesh. it was a good find and we were happy with it.
